Package com.terracottatech.store.async

Interface AsyncIntStream

All Superinterfaces:
AutoCloseable, BaseStream<Integer,AsyncIntStream>
public interface AsyncIntStream extends BaseStream<Integer,AsyncIntStream>
An asynchronous equivalent to IntStream.
